{
  "texts": [
    "The LLMs and the software engineers ought to collaboratively find out the design details that will be used in the implementation of the software system.",
    "By automating parts of the analysis, design, and coding process, LLMs allow software engineers to focus on more complex and creative aspects of software development.The contributions of this paper are as follows:• We introduced a tailored LLM for generating source code based on the provided software requirements.The LLM is fine-tuned on the knowledge, instructions, and heuristics pertinent to the software development process, requirements analysis, object-oriented design, and test-driven development.",
    "The LLM is available at https://chat.openai.com/g/g-bahoiKzkB-software- engineer-gpt.• Our innovative integration of stepwise refinement of requirements into the LLM's design process significantly enhances its robustness and accuracy.",
    "The structure of this paper is organized in the following manner: Section II examines the existing literature on generating code with LLMs.",
    "Section III presents a detailed description of our research method, outlining the systematic approach we have developed to enhance the application of LLMs in software engineering."
  ]
}